Package: covidanxietytrends
Title: Analyze Correlations Between COVID-19 Metrics and Anxiety Search Trends
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given ="Vincy",family ="Huang",, "vincyxl@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given ="Alina",family ="Hameed",, "Alina2002Hameed@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person(given ="Charlotte",family ="Ren",, "127cren@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person(given ="Alan",family ="Lee",, "alanhimself@outlook.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides tools to analyze relationships between COVID-19 public health 
    metrics (hospitalizations, vaccinations) and anxiety-related Google search trends. 
    Includes functions for data cleaning, feature selection, and visualization.
